page.title: 10Honiton:talking to Mrs Young
page.content: Wen uz cum yer, an I waz jus a med, 'unniton wadn the zame az tiz now, twaz railly ony the 'igh Strait, Noo Strait an nort elz. Now in the ot weather, the plez iz vull o'yemmits - they be paiple yer on 'oliday wot pikniks besaid the modorwez to zee the voo, an'all thay zeez is more carz........Gawky gert lummicks! If yoom lef anded down yer, uz zez yoom coochy. Us asts 'where be gwain to?' or 'Ow bee?', to which ee ansurs 'I bee, 'ow bee yoo?', but the plez is vull o' vurreners, and ee casn unerstan wot theym zayin, nor vicky verky.
